        "cooked": "<p>The Current Farsi/Persian Font is Really Awful to Read.<br>\nto Give u a visual demonstration:</p>\n<p>Roboto, “Helvetica Neue” (Signal Desktop)<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/90817b3e62b8bf3da70e602a42f9fb8c1eac8346.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/90817b3e62b8bf3da70e602a42f9fb8c1eac8346\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/90817b3e62b8bf3da70e602a42f9fb8c1eac8346.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"kCmarmAMLFaWXEouPr7eVE73Qoe\" width=\"690\" height=\"137\" data-dominant-color=\"525458\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">972×194 19.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>“Segoe UI”, Arial, sans-serif (Twitter)<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/d/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/d/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b_2_690x120.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"vNtWqbkNqNSTsVg4ocbIujzSQjN\" width=\"690\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/d/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b_2_690x120.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/d/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b_2_1035x180.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/d/dedb583e5aefc04e9dc61e39c0abac8f49667a3b.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2F3B48\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1375×241 36.1 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Tahoma, “Iranian Sans” (Wikipedia)<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d_2_690x142.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"mgElks3G8ESvaRNxiS7GJXhhQJL\" width=\"690\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d_2_690x142.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/2X/9/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d_2_1035x213.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/9/9c11ab9ecf81df706dd80718f561f7fec184294d.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2C3845\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1203×249 32.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I also made the same request on <a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/2648\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Signal-Desktop’s Github forum</a>. which is tracking (hopefully).</p>",
