        "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/anon57494327\">@anon57494327</a><br>\nI realize that, but that’s because the current font is basically Arabic (the Arabic Wikipedia uses a similar font as Signal).<br>\n<strong>Orthographically</strong> speaking this font shouldn’t even be used for Farsi/Persian,<br>\nThis might be a usual stereotype <strong>conflating</strong> these two Cultures.<br>\nThis font is <strong>Never</strong> used in Persian Media, Books etc.</p>",
