        "cooked": "<p>It’s now available in beta:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-signal_staff\" data-username=\"jamiebuilds-signal\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"57767\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/jamiebuilds-signal/48/32947_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"><a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/beta-feedback-for-the-upcoming-desktop-6-43-release/57767/1\">Beta feedback for the upcoming Desktop 6.43 Release</a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The default font for Persian has been updated to Vazirmatn to improve readability when that language is selected (Signal Settings &gt; Appearance &gt; Language). Thanks, <a href=\"https://github.com/MahdiNazemi\">@MahdiNazemi</a>!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>",
